### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

###
### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  CATEGORIES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar categorias
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar categoria - Filme
# @name createFilme
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Filme",
  "description": "A categoria mais assistida",
  "is_active": true
}

###

### Criar categoria - Documentário
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Documentário",
  "is_active": true
}

###

### Buscar categoria por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{filme_id}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar categoria
PUT {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{filme_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Long Metragem",
  "description": "Filmes longos",
  "is_active": true
}

###

### Deletar categoria
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{filme_id}}
Accept: application/json

###
### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  GENRES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar gêneros
GET {{baseUrl}}/genres
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar gênero
# @name createGenre
POST {{baseUrl}}/genres
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Ação",
  "categories_id": []
}

###

### Buscar gênero por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/genres/{{genre_id}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar gênero
PUT {{baseUrl}}/genres/{{genre_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Drama",
  "categories_id": [],
  "is_active": true
}

###

### Deletar gênero
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/genres/{{genre_id}}
Accept: application/json

###
### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  CAST MEMBERS
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar membros do elenco
GET {{baseUrl}}/cast_members
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar membro do elenco
# @name createCastMember
POST {{baseUrl}}/cast_members
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Vin Diesel",
  "type": "ACTOR"
}

###

### Buscar membro do elenco por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/cast_members/{{cast_member_id}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar membro do elenco
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cast_members/{{cast_member_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Vin Diesel",
  "type": "ACTOR"
}

###

### Deletar membro do elenco
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cast_members/{{cast_member_id}}
Accept: application/json

###
### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  VIDEOS
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar vídeos
GET {{baseUrl}}/videos
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar vídeo (sem arquivos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/videos
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Velozes e Furiosos",
  "description": "Corridas e adrenalina",
  "year_launched": 2001,
  "opened": true,
  "rating": "L",
  "duration": 106,
  "categories_id": [],
  "genres_id": [],
  "cast_members_id": []
}

###

### Buscar vídeo por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/videos/{{video_id}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar vídeo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/videos/{{video_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Velozes e Furiosos",
  "description": "Corridas e adrenalina",
  "year_launched": 2001,
  "opened": true,
  "published": true,
  "rating": "L",
  "duration": 106,
  "categories_id": [],
  "genres_id": [],
  "cast_members_id": []
}

###

### Deletar vídeo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/videos/{{video_id}}
Accept: application/json